183
00:09:41,710 --> 00:09:43,590
Would you like to go and talk to her?

184
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:45,550
Alright.

185
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:48,220
(Lake Villa)

186
00:10:02,230 --> 00:10:03,070
Your Highness,

187
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,160
