188
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:05,920
Come in.

189
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,200
Xu Qi'an, look.

190
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,320
In the capital of the Dafeng,

191
00:10:23,710 --> 00:10:25,440
even the sun is restrained.

192
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,800
I remember Pingyang once said

193
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,320
in the South, the sunset

194
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,750
could turn the whole sky red.

195
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,750
In the boundless desert,

196
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:38,990
one could chase the sun freely.

197
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:44,550
The South was

198
00:10:45,470 --> 00:10:47,830
Princess Pingyang's destination, right?

199
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:50,640
Yes.

200
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:54,920
These past few days,
I was wondering

201
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,830
whether it was worth it for Pingyang

202
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:01,110
to die for freedom.

203
00:11:02,830 --> 00:11:03,960
Have you found an answer?

204
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:07,510
Not a clue.

205
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,630
It only adds to my worries.

206
00:11:13,630 --> 00:11:14,470
Please sit.

207
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:16,280
I'd like to hear your opinion.

208
00:11:30,990 --> 00:11:32,960
I dare not comment
on Princess Pingyang rashly,

209
00:11:33,470 --> 00:11:35,350
but if I consider the situation
at that time,

210
00:11:35,830 --> 00:11:36,830
perhaps leaving

211
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:39,110
was her only choice.

212
00:11:41,230 --> 00:11:43,560
