213
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,800
but from your description,

214
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:48,590
I know she was someone carefree,

215
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:50,870
not willing to be bound by etiquette.

216
00:11:51,230 --> 00:11:52,230
For her,

217
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:54,960
marrying into the royal family
might be scarier than death.

218
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:01,380
What's wrong with marrying a prince?

219
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:03,680
