luxurious, and noble life.

220
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:07,160
This is what many ladies dream of.

221
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,680
Then they can go and be one.

222
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,710
Anyway, I don't want to.

223
00:12:12,230 --> 00:12:13,070
Listen.

224
00:12:13,350 --> 00:12:15,080
Compared with marrying
a man without love

225
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,630
and being trapped in a life of pretense,

226
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:20,280
I'd rather die.

227
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:25,230
I'll help you escape the Palace.

228
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:26,750
You're flying!

229
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,470
- Higher!
- You're flying!

230
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:43,800
I misspoke.

231
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,750
Please forgive me.

232
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,440
You're right.

233
00:12:53,830 --> 00:12:55,470
That was Pingyang's only choice.

234
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,590
It's also mine now.

235
00:13:04,350 --> 00:13:05,710
My mother once told me

236
00:13:06,280 --> 00:13:07,780
that to marry into the noble families,

237
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:08,920
to stabilize the court,

238
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,300
and to ease my father's worries,

239
00:13:11,470 --> 00:13:12,800
is the destiny of a princess.

240
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:16,200
I'm not far from that day.

241
00:13:17,990 --> 00:13:18,830
Your Highness.

242
00:13:19,350 --> 00:13:20,280
Now that you're here,

243
00:13:20,470 --> 00:13:21,630
have a drink with me.

244
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,110
Your wish is my command.

245
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:25,630
There will be fireworks later.

246
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:49,400
Your Highness,

247
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:52,080
your fireworks are different
from the ones I've seen.

248
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,400
They're quite beautiful.

249
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:10,710
Xu Qi'an,

250
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:15,750
do you think Princess Pingyang
might not have died,

251
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,920
but instead went to another world,

252
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:20,510
watching fireworks with us?

253
00:14:22,350 --> 00:14:23,190
Yes.

254
00:14:24,230 --> 00:14:25,310
In that world,

255
00:14:25,310 --> 00:14:27,370
there is no concept of ruler and subject

256
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:28,590
and of high and low.

257
00:14:28,830 --> 00:14:30,400
Everyone is born equal.

258
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:32,320
There's no such thing
as parental commands

259
00:14:32,590 --> 00:14:33,960
or arranged marriages.

260
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,990
In the sea of people,

261
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,400
if two people meet

262
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:38,870
and fall in love,

263
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:41,030
they can walk hand in hand for life.

264
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:58,990
Even if they don't meet a good match,

265
00:14:59,510 --> 00:15:01,540
there's no need to settle
due to outside pressure.

266
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:04,230
Living alone is just as good.

267
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:07,870
You can go anywhere you want

268
00:15:07,870 --> 00:15:09,590
and do whatever you want to do.

269
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:11,750
Is there really such a world?

270
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:12,640
Of course.

271
00:15:13,710 --> 00:15:15,750
Not only can women live
without marrying,

272
00:15:15,870 --> 00:15:17,110
in that world,

273
00:15:17,110 --> 00:15:18,800
women, like men,

274
00:15:18,860 --> 00:15:20,750
can go out, struggle,
and pursue their dreams,

275
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:22,110
to realize their own worth.

276
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:25,630
When they grow old,
they can buy a house with friends

277
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:27,800
and live a simple, happy life.

278
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:46,110
If such a world exists,

279
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,750
I really want to see it.

280
00:15:51,870 --> 00:15:53,080
But...

281
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:55,590
But what?

282
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:58,800
But I'm not as beautiful as Pingyang.

283
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:01,680
I'm not as smart

284
00:16:02,510 --> 00:16:03,350
as she is.

285
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:05,280
I'm not as brave as she is.

286
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:12,110
I can't do anything.

287
00:16:20,040 --> 00:16:21,110
On the contrary,

288
00:16:21,990 --> 00:16:24,630
Your Highness have many advantages.

289
00:16:25,710 --> 00:16:26,630
You're carefree,

290
00:16:27,230 --> 00:16:28,110
genuine,

291
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:29,870
and sincere toward others.

292
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:32,160
Even so,

293
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:34,750
I wouldn't want to leave the people
in this world.

294
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:37,830
I can't leave my mother,

295
00:16:39,550 --> 00:16:42,230
even though she always complains
that I'm useless.

296
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:43,710
And my brother.

297
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:45,990
Every time Mother scolds me,

298
00:16:45,990 --> 00:16:48,320
he's always the first to protect me.

299
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:50,040
And Father.

300
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:52,710
Even though I'm a useless person,

301
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,710
he still favors me.

302
00:16:56,470 --> 00:16:57,590
And Gang.

303
00:16:59,040 --> 00:16:59,920
And you.

304
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:05,990
Me too?

305
00:17:08,990 --> 00:17:10,960
Though we haven't known each other

306
00:17:11,310 --> 00:17:12,160
for long,

307
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:15,230
I really admire your nature.

308
00:17:16,360 --> 00:17:17,990
Sometimes you're as timid as a mouse,

309
00:17:18,600 --> 00:17:19,440
but sometimes

310
00:17:19,550 --> 00:17:21,130
you're bold enough to defy the heavens.

311
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:23,360
You can write poems

312
00:17:24,030 --> 00:17:25,160
and solve cases,

313
00:17:25,840 --> 00:17:27,960
and you know many interesting things.

314
00:17:30,710 --> 00:17:31,790
You also know

315
00:17:31,790 --> 00:17:34,200
that I love the egg-yolk puff
from Shop of Delicacies.

316
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:38,710
Mother says they're too greasy
and doesn't let me eat them.

317
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:40,790
I have to sneak out of the Palace

318
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,990
to buy them myself every time.

319
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:46,790
How do you know?

320
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:53,600
She'll understand after seeing it.

321
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:55,660
(Shop of Delicacies)

322
00:17:59,230 --> 00:18:01,960
Someone who secretly cares about you

323
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:03,360
told me.

324
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,790
Impossible.

325
00:18:06,750 --> 00:18:08,310
Pingyang is dead.

326
00:18:08,990 --> 00:18:10,510
I have no friends left.

327
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:13,470
Your Highness, you're drunk.

328
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,840
Your Highness, if you don't mind,

329
00:18:27,270 --> 00:18:28,160
from now on,

330
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,920
I can be your friend.

331
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:55,230
I don't want to be your friend.

332
00:18:56,150 --> 00:18:58,440
♪The sky is clear now;
the clouds are gone♪

333
00:18:58,820 --> 00:19:01,810
♪No more cold starts at night♪

334
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:04,930
♪Quietly waiting
for the flowers to bloom♪

335
00:19:05,150 --> 00:19:09,190
♪Chasing the south wind
through a quiet garden♪

336
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:11,880
♪Among all the worldly sights♪

337
00:19:12,180 --> 00:19:15,120
♪Only you are the hardest to find♪

338
00:19:26,470 --> 00:19:29,480
♪Thousands of words♪

339
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:31,910
♪For you, I can become Li Bai♪

340
00:19:31,910 --> 00:19:34,850
♪Thousands of thoughts as the preface♪

341
00:19:34,850 --> 00:19:37,060
♪Half a poem still depicts my feelings♪

342
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:39,950
♪Thousands of simple words
make a poem♪

343
00:19:40,170 --> 00:19:42,580
♪To express my devotion to you♪

344
00:19:42,580 --> 00:19:45,390
♪Thousands of thoughts as the preface♪

345
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:47,740
♪Half a poem still depicts my feelings♪

346
00:19:47,740 --> 00:19:50,610
♪Thousands of simple words make a poem♪

347
00:19:50,890 --> 00:19:53,450
♪To express my devotion to you♪

348
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:55,790
♪All the scenes in this world♪

349
00:19:55,790 --> 00:19:58,380
♪Are beautiful because of you♪

350
00:19:58,380 --> 00:20:01,310
♪Thousands of words♪
♪How to express my longing poetically♪

351
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:03,900
♪For you, I can become Li Bai♪
♪I once read poems♪

352
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:06,840
♪Thousands of words♪
♪But even Li Bai couldn't portrait you♪

353
00:20:06,840 --> 00:20:09,230
♪Half a poem still depicts my feelings♪
♪Took all the words♪

354
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:12,230
♪Thousands of simple words make a poem♪
♪Love is a mysterious fate♪

355
00:20:12,230 --> 00:20:14,760
♪To express my devotion to you♪
♪Can't compare to true love♪

356
00:20:14,890 --> 00:20:17,230
♪All the scenes in this world♪
♪I'd use the rivers as ink♪

357
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:20,830
♪Are beautiful because of you♪
♪To write about my longing for you♪

358
00:20:35,010 --> 00:20:36,440
Your Highness, you're awake.

359
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:38,310
Take it slow.

360
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:40,360
Take it slow. How do you feel?

361
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:45,400
I've been sleeping here all night?

362
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:46,680
Yes.

363
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:52,910
Where is Xu Qi'an?

364
00:20:53,270 --> 00:20:55,550
Xu Qi'an left before dawn.

365
00:20:56,070 --> 00:20:57,640
He stayed with you all night yesterday

366
00:20:57,880 --> 00:20:58,720
and

367
00:20:58,920 --> 00:21:00,640
held your hand the whole time.

368
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:03,720
He...

369
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:04,680
He...

370
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:06,680
Did he take advantage of me
while I was asleep?

371
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:07,640
No, no.

372
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:09,120
He was keeping you warm,

373
00:21:09,120 --> 00:21:10,640
driving away the cold.

374
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,440
Before he left, he specifically told me

375
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:17,960
that once you woke up,
you should drink this congee.

376
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:20,010
It helps sober you up
and warm your stomach.

377
00:21:20,710 --> 00:21:21,550
Try it.

378
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:23,310
He also said

379
00:21:23,310 --> 00:21:24,960
that he made it himself

380
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:27,120
and added some special ingredients

381
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:28,350
called

382
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:30,230
something like chicken powder.

383
00:21:37,230 --> 00:21:38,440
It's quite tasty.

384
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:40,240
This little brat.

385
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,750
He always has something new.

386
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:47,620
(Act if you want it.)

387
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:54,150
Senior Yang,

388
00:21:54,150 --> 00:21:56,510
(Guardians' Notice)
these are copied from the city gates.

389
00:21:56,510 --> 00:21:58,120
It indeed details

390
00:21:58,120 --> 00:21:59,680
the heroic actions of Yang Qianhuan

391
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:01,640
from the Astronomical Bureau
in this case.

392
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:03,430
It says you made a great contribution.

393
00:22:08,070 --> 00:22:11,840
I suppose my fame has spread
throughout the capital.

394
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:14,990
Thanks to the Supervisor
for calling me back

395
00:22:14,990 --> 00:22:17,300
(Guardians' Notice)
to make contributions.

396
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:18,150
My Master

397
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:20,160
truly didn't deceive me.

398
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:22,990
But

399
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:25,030
I'll have to be more careful

400
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:26,750
when I go out

401
00:22:26,750 --> 00:22:28,470
to avoid being recognized

402
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:31,200
and causing unnecessary trouble.

403
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:33,710
There's no need for that.

404
00:22:34,230 --> 00:22:35,070
After all,

405
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:37,400
no one is talking about this.

406
00:22:39,230 --> 00:22:40,070
Why?

407
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:43,120
Senior Yang,

408
00:22:45,120 --> 00:22:46,070
this is the poem.

409
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:50,310
Since it was spread from the court,

410
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:53,060
it's caused a huge stir
in the Directorate of Education

411
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:54,920
and Yunlu Academy.

412
00:22:55,230 --> 00:22:56,160
It's been hailed

413
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:59,200
as the greatest satire poem ever.

414
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:01,680
Now it's spread everywhere.

415
00:23:01,990 --> 00:23:05,550
Everyone praises Mr. Xu
as the Dafeng's conscience.

416
00:23:05,750 --> 00:23:08,600
I only wish my child
to be foolish and simple,

417
00:23:09,360 --> 00:23:10,750
without disaster or hardship,

418
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:13,230
to become a public official.

419
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:15,120
Why?

420
00:23:15,960 --> 00:23:17,790
Why is it that Xu Ningyan

421
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:21,600
can always do things

422
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:24,440
that everyone envies?

423
00:23:26,750 --> 00:23:29,470
He single-handedly solved
the Sangbo Case

424
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,790
and scolded the powerful

425
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:33,920
when he was beneath everyone.

426
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,270
It's not fair.

427
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:39,440
It's not fair.

428
00:23:40,840 --> 00:23:43,260
It's so unfair.

429
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,520
Senior Yang,

430
00:23:45,300 --> 00:23:46,310
are you alright?

431
00:23:48,740 --> 00:23:49,640
I have

432
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:52,960
realized it.

433
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:56,270
I'm going to stand before the court

434
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:57,600
and scold the officials.

435
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:59,790
If Xu Ningyan is
the Dafeng's conscience,

436
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:01,990
then I want to be the Dafeng's light,

437
00:24:01,990 --> 00:24:03,200
shining before the court.

438
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,440
Senior Yang, don't.

439
00:24:08,510 --> 00:24:10,840
Holding the sun and moon,
I pluck the stars.

440
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:13,920
There is no one like me in this world.

441
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,230
Who brought me here?

442
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:20,170
Master, are you going to stop me?

443
00:24:20,470 --> 00:24:21,880
You're being too impatient.

444
00:24:22,070 --> 00:24:24,790
You said I'd be famous once I go back.

445
00:24:25,230 --> 00:24:26,770
Why are you stopping me now?

446
00:24:26,770 --> 00:24:28,310
The capital is full of hidden talents.

447
00:24:28,310 --> 00:24:30,120
There's always someone better.

448
00:24:30,550 --> 00:24:31,390
Master,

449
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:33,310
explain clearly.

450
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:35,070
I mean

451
00:24:35,070 --> 00:24:36,990
you should hide your weaknesses.

452
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:39,150
I have

453
00:24:39,310 --> 00:24:40,200
realized it.

454
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:41,600
What have you realized?

455
00:24:41,600 --> 00:24:43,990
Master, are you stopping me

456
00:24:44,310 --> 00:24:46,310
because you're afraid I'll outshine you?

457
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:53,600
Old man,

458
00:24:53,600 --> 00:24:55,470
let me out!

459
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:57,640
Old man!

460
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,160
It's my turn.

461
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:12,960
I've just finished

462
00:25:13,070 --> 00:25:14,920
handling a small matter.

463
00:25:15,120 --> 00:25:16,460
Your Highness, please forgive me.

464
00:25:18,030 --> 00:25:19,790
Supervisor, your chess skills

465
00:25:20,070 --> 00:25:21,120
aren't as good as before.

466
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,280
But

467
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:26,360
your ability to judge people

468
00:25:26,750 --> 00:25:28,510
is still as sharp as ever.

469
00:25:29,030 --> 00:25:29,990
Xu Qi'an

470
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:31,880
did solve the case.

471
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:33,790
He didn't fail you.

472
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:37,270
First, you let me introduce him
to the Guardians,

473
00:25:37,550 --> 00:25:39,710
and you guided him step by step

474
00:25:39,710 --> 00:25:40,710
to solve the Sangbo Case.

475
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:42,070
But

476
00:25:42,990 --> 00:25:45,440
isn't that a bit too early?

477
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:48,790
I have no other choice.

478
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:51,120
The Nine Pass is full of villains.

479
00:25:51,710 --> 00:25:52,960
Only in this way

480
00:25:53,750 --> 00:25:54,680
can he fight

481
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:56,070
with them.

482
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:00,640
As you say, Supervisor.

483
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:02,600
But there is one thing.

484
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:05,070
Unless absolutely necessary,

485
00:26:05,510 --> 00:26:07,510
don't involve Lin'an.

486
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:12,200
You're right, Your Highness.

487
00:26:12,470 --> 00:26:13,600
I'll remember that.

488
00:26:25,990 --> 00:26:26,830
Good move.

489
00:26:29,900 --> 00:26:36,900
(Xu Mansion)

490
00:26:39,030 --> 00:26:39,870
Honey,

491
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:43,030
have you told Cijiu that we've moved?

492
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:43,870
Don't worry.

493
00:26:44,070 --> 00:26:45,600
Ningyan is reliable.

494
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:47,920
He must've written to the Academy.

495
00:26:48,750 --> 00:26:49,920
Welcome.

496
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:51,310
Congratulations.

497
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:52,310
You're here.

498
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:54,200
Yes, now your family

499
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,440
has two talents.

500
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,470
From now on,

501
00:26:56,470 --> 00:26:58,880
you'll live a life
of endless wealth and honor.

502
00:26:58,880 --> 00:27:00,540
- No.
- This is a perfect gift

503
00:27:00,540 --> 00:27:01,710
(Nourishing Cream)
for you.

504
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:03,500
Try this cream.
It's perfect for your skin.

505
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:05,130
Your skin will be as smooth and bright

506
00:27:05,130 --> 00:27:05,870
as white jade.

507
00:27:05,990 --> 00:27:08,270
Thanks. This is really good.

508
00:27:08,710 --> 00:27:10,510
Wealth and honor are beyond our reach.

509
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:12,230
We're just getting by.

510
00:27:12,230 --> 00:27:13,160
Getting by?

511
00:27:13,230 --> 00:27:14,550
You call this getting by?

512
00:27:14,550 --> 00:27:16,160
Look at the house you chose.

513
00:27:16,160 --> 00:27:17,230
It's quiet yet convenient,

514
00:27:17,230 --> 00:27:18,510
a perfect retreat.

515
00:27:18,510 --> 00:27:20,230
Living here must be comfortable.

516
00:27:20,230 --> 00:27:21,270
Come on.

517
00:27:21,270 --> 00:27:22,840
It's quite secluded.

518
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,400
From East City to West City,

519
00:27:25,550 --> 00:27:27,920
the coachman took an hour to find here.

520
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:28,790
I got dizzy

521
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:30,030
from all the turning.

522
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:33,600
If you don't feel well,

523
00:27:33,600 --> 00:27:34,790
you should go rest

524
00:27:34,790 --> 00:27:35,920
and eat something.

525
00:27:36,070 --> 00:27:37,680
Never mind. I'm not hungry.

526
00:27:38,030 --> 00:27:40,120
I had a bird's nest and snow frog stew
for breakfast.

527
00:27:40,120 --> 00:27:41,310
It hasn't been digested yet.

528
00:27:42,790 --> 00:27:44,030
Don't let her get to you.

529
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:46,790
Her husband used to work
in the Ministry of Rites.

530
00:27:46,790 --> 00:27:48,160
Because of the Sangbo Case,

531
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:50,330
he's still detained
in the Ministry of Justice.

532
00:27:50,360 --> 00:27:52,310
How could she be in the mood
to eat anything?

533
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:55,120
It's just a routine inquiry.

534
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:56,880
He'll be back in a few days.

535
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,550
Didn't you just tell me

536
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:00,260
that this time he's in trouble,

537
00:28:00,260 --> 00:28:01,790
and you were trying to ask Xu Ningyan

538
00:28:01,790 --> 00:28:03,200
to intercede for him?

539
00:28:04,750 --> 00:28:05,920
Ridiculous.

540
00:28:06,310 --> 00:28:09,120
Xu Ningyan is just a Copper Gong.

541
00:28:09,470 --> 00:28:10,680
He can't possibly

542
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:12,550
have a say in such a matter.

543
00:28:12,550 --> 00:28:14,920
The Guardians are here.

544
00:28:36,700 --> 00:28:38,820
(Xu Mansion)

545
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:51,750
Mr. Yang, Mr. Nangong.

546
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:53,990
Sorry for the improper welcome.

547
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,160
Mr. Xu,

548
00:28:56,360 --> 00:28:57,610
on behalf of the Guardians,

549
00:28:57,610 --> 00:28:59,880
we're here to congratulate you
on moving to a new house.

550
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:02,470
Thank you.

551
00:29:02,960 --> 00:29:04,440
It's truly an honor

552
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:06,790
for our family to have you here.

553
00:29:06,790 --> 00:29:08,470
We're truly honored.

554
00:29:15,070 --> 00:29:16,840
Where is Lord Wei?

555
00:29:17,270 --> 00:29:18,470
Lord Wei said he'd come.

556
00:29:19,750 --> 00:29:20,710
Lord Wei is busy,

557
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:22,680
so he asked us to come

558
00:29:22,960 --> 00:29:24,510
and congratulate you on his behalf.

559
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:27,750
We understand.

560
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:28,710
Everyone,

561
00:29:28,710 --> 00:29:29,920
please, come inside.

562
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:31,400
We still have matters to attend to,

563
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,160
so we won't trouble you further.

564
00:29:37,030 --> 00:29:38,440
- Goodbye.
- Safe travels.

565
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:40,160
- Congrats, Mr. Xu.
- Thank you.

